Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能遇上你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处女座的我  不得不感慨伤感的命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  是因为没有释放光粒子  才被发现的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是后者吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被完全压制了！不过！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的庞然大物可打不中我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一块装甲碎片归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是光束军刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武装组织  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣言要根除全世界战争的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并开始进行武装干预
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干预了印度南部锡兰岛的民族纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而震惊世界的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到了新的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神对于人类的制裁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是  变革的序曲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}#03 变化的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  你真是个无法预测的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了来复枪  又得写检讨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次战斗所获得的Gundam的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使损失了一台Flag  也是赚的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借和他接触时弄上去的涂料  也许能够追踪到他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  还真年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他对话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的动作里蕴含着感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam  追踪失败
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独出击…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Flag  到底是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现场特派员联络上了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Gundam啊  小点也没关系  把画像先放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being没有进行声明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  十分钟以内开始播放特别报道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一条新闻是现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几小时内  人革主席将会发表官方声明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把版面空出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稿子做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…绢江…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是21世纪后期出现的绝无仅有的发明之王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倡导了太阳光发电系统的基础理论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从来不抛头露面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他的大名流传后世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他创建了Celestial Being的话  还是可信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是才能还是资金方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么200多年以后的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们才开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格家族的血缘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他那一代完全断绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:08.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}AEU  谍报机关本部  长官室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的资产流向了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的记录里什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是故意做了手脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21世纪的情报安全系统可是摆设一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being他们做得很周全  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官您认为他们的武力干预会一直继续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果换成是我  一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我把议会报告用的资料做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口也帮我找好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:38.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,0)}人革联  轨道电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天柱交通公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘E273号班次的旅客们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在A12号门集合  谢谢您的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个好胜的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经向吠陀上交了报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会我会看一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事比什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙那边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去执行下一个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会遵从命令的  虽然有不定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真的做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用轨道电梯把机体送回宇宙这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照原计划  把它们混进了殖民地开发用的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重量一样  只要能搬进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的检查就没什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在这个地方进行检查的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个盲点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们如果说有弱点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是没有Gundam就会像普特利麦奥斯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动时间被限制到了极点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有区区四个太阳炉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机密情报不要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚的列车到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天柱交通公司的E277班次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将于预定时刻  14点18分…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连向宇宙的直线通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌地面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能稍微休息一会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁热打铁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一两次的话  世界可是不会认同我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候已久  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重力的地方真是舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很能体会您的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  司令正在等着  请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我想到锡兰去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是只相信亲眼所见的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令也应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我陪您前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:16.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,300)}联合  MSWAD总部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是AEU新机型的发布会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果发生了不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然存在那样的机体  真是难以想象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常有研究价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高层也是这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给亲眼看到Gundam的你们两个下达了调职命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「对Gundam调查队」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新设立的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式名称之后将由司令部命名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷夫·埃夫曼教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来担任技术主任吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高层就是这么重视这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快给我搞定它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利·片桐技术顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受对Gundam调查队的调职命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经预见到这样的事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那么大的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得这就是缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱尔兰的阿尔斯特地区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是零散的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但恐怖行动持续了将近4世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Catholic Protestant{\fsp225}　{\r}\N虽说是天主教和新教的基督教两个派别对立而引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两派的矛盾似乎还远不止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的论文就以北爱尔兰的对立为主题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是论文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是工学部  为什么要有历史课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「之后的技术革命将以轨道电梯的维持和太空殖民地开发为中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以与各国技术者的交流为目的  培养历史观也是有必要的」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然能够理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  托这个福  我才能留学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点倒是很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年后  留学生活也就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈考虑过将来的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有把我考虑进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一会  路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的时候应该追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只点了软饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的推荐可是原味鸡尾酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可还没成年哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上第三个任务就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要看的话  建议您准备3个显示器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那还真是期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偷窥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:44.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,300)}锡兰岛内\N人革联  驻军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  有搞清楚什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是谢尔盖中校  请说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是MS的爆击用功能组件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材质是E Carbon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是最新的原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在结构上并未确认有新技术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那所搭载的导弹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  通过调查残留物得知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是300km左右的制导导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  没有开发此类型的国家和制造商
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是独自开发的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从机体所受的冲击度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的输出功率有Flag的6倍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底装了什么马达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是那种输出功率  还有那机动性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用战斗数据确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现那种机动性的果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  从Gundam的机体释放出类似发光粒子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可算是令人信服的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被雷达和传感器探测到  是因为这个原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种特殊粒子除了用于隐形外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用于机体控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕还能用于武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷夫·埃夫曼教授
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个可怕的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有比我们先进几十年的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在Celestial Being的罪行声明中露面的历史人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太阳光发电系统的倡导者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谍报部好像在根据这一线索来追查Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个组件也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不错的技术在使用中被抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能办到的话  真想捕获到它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那称作Gundam的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  想拜托调试一下这个机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对机师的负担呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用考虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  希望时限是一周
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真会乱讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不稍微强行点的话  就无法吸引Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他完全被迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  Gundam出现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有两个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲南部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是对由矿物资源的开采权引起的内战的武力干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:38.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}非洲南部地区  矿物资源开采现场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种欺凌弱小的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快解除武装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了  逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一台是在塔利比亚  可以从这边过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从心底里讨厌毒品等东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要烧掉的话  我希望能支持Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是要根除纷争的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘旋行动自开始已进行30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:35.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}南美  塔利比亚上空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirios  现在开始作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标达成率为97%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这种事  随时都可以办到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三台出现在这锡兰岛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是第七驻地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使用的铁人还有吗  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校亲自去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的  我只相信亲眼所见之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物吗  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  继续介入纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击  射击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一阶段结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…Gundam吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢掉了枪械？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想试探我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见识一下根绝战争什么的觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要肉的话就给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个头部  归我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达汇合点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已目测确认Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始返舰准备  相对引导系统工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输器  打开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联动系统良好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  返舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返舰完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue的GN驱动器  开始与普特利麦奥斯的连接操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Virtue向托勒密传输能量准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始传输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是宇宙好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来吧  干下杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  行不通…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你是旁边房间的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与姐姐两个人在这房间一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是刹那·F·清荣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清荣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  有工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这阵子比较忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于Celestial Being的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭随便吃点吧  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沙慈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看新闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了  看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天凌晨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北爱尔兰的恐怖组织——真IRA正式发表宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将基于武力的恐怖活动完全冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续了400年的北爱尔兰纷争  实际上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将开辟通向新的和平的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天作业的论文会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  在改变…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用Celestial Being的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及利用该国的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister在奔赴充满阴谋的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「对外交涉」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓政治  就如同变幻无穷的万花筒


